<body>
    <p><strong>Sensor Configuration Page </strong></p>
<p>This screen will allow you to configure sensors for a particular site</p>

<p>Click on the sensor location on the map</p>

<p>Select the Hub Id configured for the selected site from the drop down list</p>

<p>Enter the Senosr Id, the Minimum Threshold Level and Maximum Threshold Level and click on the 'Add Sensor' button</p>

<p>Delete the Sensor Details by clicking on the <i class='fa fa-minus-square'></i> icon</p>

<p>Click on the 'Close' button to complete the Sensor configuration process and go back to the List of Sites Page</p>

</body>
</html>
